    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 塔拉拉星系，一个依靠垂死恒星的能量延续生命，却因最后的燃料「星辉矿（Starium）」而四分五裂的银河。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名初来乍到的探索者，你将踏入危机四伏的星球，做出影响派系存亡的抉择，并在险境中求生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会选择拯救银河、趁乱逐利，还是开辟属于自己的道路？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/b0c1d7b1cb05800f7acff8ce8a6889b3.avif?t=1772024118\" width=471 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塔拉拉是一个充满无限可能与巨大代价的领域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在它的核心，稀有燃料「星辉矿」自垂死恒星中开采而出，既推动了文明的进步，也引发了毁灭性的冲突。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个动荡的前沿，你将面对危险、机遇与道德困境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会崛起为救世主、冷酷的掌控者，还是创造属于自己的未知命运？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/e2902464f856e646b8684b4e43bbca28.avif?t=1772024118\" width=471 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个道德复杂的宇宙中，每一个选择都举足轻重。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的行动将掀起涟漪，塑造联盟、点燃冲突，并最终改写银河的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索细致入微的 像素艺术世界「拉拉星（Rhalara）」，一个充满危险、奇迹与秘密等待揭开的星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/c9b9c2fba112132a237e878561f6f702.poster.avif?t=1772024118\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/c9b9c2fba112132a237e878561f6f702.webm?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/c9b9c2fba112132a237e878561f6f702.mp4?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/4482dd9702e5b9ea02ceb594b968cb0a.avif?t=1772024118\" width=470 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你邂逅的将有 自由战士、财阀巨头、流浪冒险者，以及 神秘的外星派系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定你要信任谁、背叛谁，又将与谁并肩作战，共同决定塔拉拉的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/d7620a0d1afe12070b4fc042ab33ea4c.poster.avif?t=1772024118\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/d7620a0d1afe12070b4fc042ab33ea4c.webm?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/d7620a0d1afe12070b4fc042ab33ea4c.mp4?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/8b1ecb966f06f942aa525b97b25ff36e.avif?t=1772024118\" width=471 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的生存方式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为 正直的英雄，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐秘的渗透者，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和平的谈判者，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或是 无情的毁灭者。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择将塑造声望、关系与故事走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在希望与毁灭之间摇摆的银河中，留下你的印记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/93f10ae9d56d540a2c4317f38ef5fded.poster.avif?t=1772024118\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/93f10ae9d56d540a2c4317f38ef5fded.webm?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/93f10ae9d56d540a2c4317f38ef5fded.mp4?t=1772024118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3327700/extras/d99613d1c299889ed30eb37e982562e3.avif?t=1772024118\" width=471 height=74 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索庞大的星球：踏遍多样区域，揭开秘密、异常现象与远古遗迹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 战术性战斗：在策略驱动的激烈战斗中，对抗无情的派系、外星掠食者和敌对探索者。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自定义与成长：解锁强力装备、武器与技能，打造专属的游戏风格。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 动态对话选择：多分支对话系统将影响你的盟友、敌人，乃至整个银河的命运。</p></li></ul>",
